{"tid":685661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】美國明天(1/6)起向歐盟 加拿大 墨西哥徵收鋼鋁關稅　招反彈","createTime":"2018-05-31T14:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T15:05:04.000Z","uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"44417607907e50168a8fc32fc702388674cd806c","tid":685661,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰】美明起向歐盟加墨徵鋼鋁稅　招反彈<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：2018/05/31 22:15<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部長羅斯（Wilbur Ross）今天宣布，6月1日起向歐洲、加拿大及墨西哥分別徵收25%鋼鐵及10%鋁材關稅。另外他擬於周五訪問中國。歐盟執委會主席榮克表示，完全無法接受，將在數小時內立刻提出反擊措施，直言這是「全球貿易糟糕的一天」。墨西哥隨即宣布報復措施。<br />\n美國總統川普今年3月宣布向鋼鐵及鋁材分別徵收25%及10%進口關稅，但對歐盟、澳洲及加拿大等盟友提供豁免至本周五。如今決定取消豁免。美國此舉被視為是實踐總統川普長期以來保護美國產業的承諾，羅斯聲稱，即使引發盟友報復，對美國也不至於造成太大影響。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會今天表示，在美國祭出關稅動作後，歐盟將別無選擇，但將採取行動保護產業、工作機會和利益。歐盟貿易事務執委馬姆斯壯（Cecilia Malmstrom）發表聲明，歐盟將向世貿組織提出申訴，要求爭端解決。德國總理梅克爾則說，歐盟會以「堅定團結」應對美方措施。<br />\n<br />\n英國也表示，對美國的決定「深感失望」，政府發言人表示「英國和其他歐盟國家是美國緊密的盟國，應該永久且完全豁免於美國關鋁稅」。<br />\n<br />\n較早前有媒體報導，美國有意提早向歐洲鋼、鋁徵收關稅，另有報導指，川普有意令德國汽車「退出」美國市場。<br />\n（國際中心／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180531/1364976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180531%2F1364976&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1ddc5b24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180531%2F1364976&h=7cb2c421\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180531/1364976</a>"},{"pid":"7e90b4b766b8189f33c60d0739a063ee4754c78c","tid":685661,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87a269591b063e55dc5585fce36480152dff0ed","tid":685661,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"美帝公佈完收中国關稅<br />\n不過開始收咗中国關稅未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁快就搵盟友開刀"},{"pid":"c5721d31d7add21fa0b78382daf1dd028522a526","tid":685661,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e87a269591b063e55dc5585fce36480152dff0ed","tid":685661,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"美帝公佈完收中国關稅<br />\n不過開始收咗中国關稅未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁快就搵盟友開刀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"美國共和黨的著名反中共議員Marco Rubio: 美國不要對歐洲和亞洲其他國家開刀, 否則只會迫使這些國家跟中共合作.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1002133316164816896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1002133316164816896&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=44ce2d04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1002133316164816896&h=a58e912f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1002133316164816896</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMarco Rubio<br />\n&rlm;Verified account @marcorubio<br />\n<br />\nEu&shy;rope &amp; Asia also have major concerns about #China stealing &amp; unfair practices. But instead of joining us to confront China, our tariffs against them is making it easier for China to line them up against us. #BeSmart #BeStrategic<br />\n<br />\n3:22 AM - 31 May 2018"},{"pid":"33ccc9ebdb82161b91fa3625b11d8865748e3978","tid":685661,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc15774ec989eb4257571374d1a2e0041b159db9","tid":685661,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"當奴浸搞乜鳩雖呀"},{"pid":"77736e34c34fe283863058cd1c3819fc4d1130da","tid":685661,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:03:24.000Z","msg":"歐盟 加拿大 墨西哥可能會同中國組成復仇者聯盟對抗美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff820da931514f94392c965ec2d9e3492ad755de","tid":685661,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"侵侵又撚狗？"},{"pid":"a5ce35fc5620637e77f9e98bdc66a643e6a37b35","tid":685661,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"佢就係想乜都美國自己做返 本地人個個有野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a887073da6ddf796a7c397f3126408be0544f9","tid":685661,"uid":182475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:18:05.000Z","msg":"好攪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/31/cramer-europeans-are-in-over-their-heads-with-trump-over-trade.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2Fcramer-europeans-are-in-over-their-heads-with-trump-over-trade.html&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=717fa4a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/31/cramer-europeans-are-in-over-their-heads-with-trump-over-trade.html</a><br />\n<br />\nCramer: Europeans are in 'over their heads' on trade because they've never seen anything like Trump<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The Europeans don't know what to do. I think they're a little taken by surprise,&quot; says Cramer, referring to the tariffs on Canada, Mexico and the EU.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Whatever the Europeans are doing, they are confused because they've never seen anything like this president,&quot; he adds."},{"pid":"57437b4c122ef8e37329ac63de3bb1f4a3fc18b7","tid":685661,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a887073da6ddf796a7c397f3126408be0544f9","tid":685661,"uid":182475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:18:05.000Z","msg":"好攪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/31/cramer-europeans-are-in-over-their-heads-with-trump-over-trade.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2Fcramer-europeans-are-in-over-their-heads-with-trump-over-trade.html&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=717fa4a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/31/cramer-europeans-are-in-over-their-heads-with-trump-over-trade.html</a><br />\n<br />\nCramer: Europeans are in 'over their heads' on trade because they've never seen anything like Trump<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The Europeans don't know what to do. I think they're a little taken by surprise,&quot; says Cramer, referring to the tariffs on Canada, Mexico and the EU.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Whatever the Europeans are doing, they are confused because they've never seen anything like this president,&quot; he adds."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"曲線幫中國組成復仇者聯盟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This is dumb. Europe, Canada, and Mexico are not China, and you don&rsquo;t treat allies the same way you treat opponents.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/frankthorp/status/1002203382520655874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffrankthorp%2Fstatus%2F1002203382520655874&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=cff64cf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffrankthorp%2Fstatus%2F1002203382520655874&h=450dbeda\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/frankthorp/status/1002203382520655874</a>"},{"pid":"e8fb77e5e8982a7c59c12e84aba3d55634a86580","tid":685661,"uid":56163,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾左膠同低等墨西哥人, 佢哋淨係識得阻住地球轉, 制裁佢哋先之後再制裁支那,trump 而家係到淨化緊地球嘅癌細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c75cede6d8ef87ef0ff3eebf138bc306174060","tid":685661,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5721d31d7add21fa0b78382daf1dd028522a526","tid":685661,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e87a269591b063e55dc5585fce36480152dff0ed","tid":685661,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"美帝公佈完收中国關稅<br />\n不過開始收咗中国關稅未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁快就搵盟友開刀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"美國共和黨的著名反中共議員Marco Rubio: 美國不要對歐洲和亞洲其他國家開刀, 否則只會迫使這些國家跟中共合作.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1002133316164816896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1002133316164816896&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=44ce2d04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1002133316164816896&h=a58e912f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1002133316164816896</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMarco Rubio<br />\n&rlm;Verified account @marcorubio<br />\n<br />\nEu&shy;rope &amp; Asia also have major concerns about #China stealing &amp; unfair practices. But instead of joining us to confront China, our tariffs against them is making it easier for China to line them up against us. #BeSmart #BeStrategic<br />\n<br />\n3:22 AM - 31 May 2018"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"佢都幾多大陸fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3387a45c910e238241c748b830dd5f54b0a12d9","tid":685661,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5ce35fc5620637e77f9e98bdc66a643e6a37b35","tid":685661,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"佢就係想乜都美國自己做返 本地人個個有野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:51:08.000Z","msg":"戇鳩，一陣逼到歐洲同大陸聯盟就仆街啦"},{"pid":"e808d1441c0bee59a9db841b053e4afb08db29dd","tid":685661,"uid":181649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5ce35fc5620637e77f9e98bdc66a643e6a37b35","tid":685661,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"佢就係想乜都美國自己做返 本地人個個有野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:16:10.000Z","msg":"巴打你真係風趣, 2002年, 喬治布殊都玩過關稅, 佢當時一度向鐵徵收30%關稅, 據事後美國國際貿易委員會研究, 由於關稅對本地製鐵產業嘅加乘, 畀對其他行業嘅衝擊抵消有突, 結果係GDP淨損失30M<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個原理其實係咁, 以鐵為例, 因為關稅, 本地鐵變相平左, 製鐵業競爭力上升, 而有誘因去請人擴張. 但另一邊廂, 本地用鐵嘅行業, 會因為成本上升, 為左維持利潤而要加價, 但會嚇走部分消費者, 最後某啲公司就會有壓力要cut人減成本<br />\n<br />\n你覺得係製鐵業多人, 定用鐵嘅行業多人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但最大鑊嘅係, 上面係未計潛在出口影響, 據美國International Trade Administration計算, 上年美國入口鐵中, 加拿大同墨西哥加埋佔26%; 但佢地加埋上年食返88%美國出口鐵, 如果佢地玩攪炒(加拿大有9成鐵都係輸出去美國, 5成入口鐵來自美國, 我查唔到老墨), 收返美國鐵關稅, 咁就真係玉石俱焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲未計連喬治布殊當年玩關稅, 都無向加拿大呢個美國最親近嘅盟友開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年點完? 喬治布殊本來想收3年, 但面對EU反擊, WTO施壓力同發現有反效果三重打擊, 收左18個月就收檔<br />\n<br />\n下面兩篇文都係借古鑑今, 由回顧喬治布殊關稅戰, 到檢視Trump今次關稅戰, 上面有興趣可以一讀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Z8GbK8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZ8GbK8&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=191b59fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Z8GbK8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/A8C9A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FA8C9A1&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5796b91b\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/A8C9A1</a><br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔識經濟學"},{"pid":"c9058c98f36bac8b43a58a4be1e37d0aff417b98","tid":685661,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676f0f349cb0f6d5eb9d70249ca0fbf182b35db9","tid":685661,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:29:48.000Z","msg":"唔係掛 搞加拿大？"},{"pid":"841ccef48eebf413172c36e737b3a7621dd9fc3e","tid":685661,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"676f0f349cb0f6d5eb9d70249ca0fbf182b35db9","tid":685661,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:29:48.000Z","msg":"唔係掛 搞加拿大？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:31:04.000Z","msg":"加拿大係咁幫支那做轉口呀"},{"pid":"31b9841575de73d85a2204c908b6b2a9c3305f9e","tid":685661,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:32:59.000Z","msg":"奶共的下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牆頭草被迫要表明立場"},{"pid":"e1380451abbd349ab88df241363ef3221f2229f0","tid":685661,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31b9841575de73d85a2204c908b6b2a9c3305f9e","tid":685661,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:32:59.000Z","msg":"奶共的下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牆頭草被迫要表明立場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:36:45.000Z","msg":"德國同加拿大兩個左膠大國"},{"pid":"d3843462aea7ff194b259888c5a2314f00b18627","tid":685661,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T18:37:01.000Z","msg":"迫班歐豬埋堆插死終蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bom